      "content": "it just feels like a lie. people say \"it gets better\" but they're just saying that to feel better themselves. how can it get better when everyone already knows the worst thing about me? even a counselor is just gonna see me as a victim or a joke. i just want the noise to stop. i want to stop feeling like every single person is judging me. is there even a way out of this feeling?",
